<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Eyes Checking</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
        text-decoration: none;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      .MainBox {
        width: 100%;
        height: 350px;
        background-color: brown;
        position: relative;
      }
      .icon {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        width: 110px;
        height: 110px;
        opacity: 0;
      }

      .icon_box1 {
        background-image: url("/image/witness.png");
        background-size: 100% 100%;
        opacity: 1;
      }

      .icon_box2 {
        background-image: url("/image/hidden.png");
        background-size: 100% 100%;
      }

      .MainBox:hover .icon_box2 {
        opacity: 1;
      }
      .MainBox:hover .icon_box1 {
        opacity: 0;
      }

      .container {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .editBtn {
        display: block;
        width: 300px;
        height: 80px;
        background-color: aqua;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 80px;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-top: 80px;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .report {
        display: block;
        width: 300px;
        height: 80px;
        background-color: red;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 80px;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-top: 30px;
        color: #000;
      }

      p {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="MainBox">
      <div class="icon_box1 icon"></div>
      <div class="icon_box2 icon"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <a class="editBtn" href="/edit">보호자 등록</a>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <a class="report" style="color: #fff" href="/report">긴급신고</a>
      <p>
        보호자 등록을 하지 않고 신고버튼을 누르면
        <span style="color: red">119</span>에 자동으로 신고가 들어갑니다.
      </p>
    </div>
    <script>
	setInterval(() => {
   	 location.reload();
 	 }, 500);
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
